summary: Just enter the bat file and have EVERY KEY
descriptionHtml: This download is a notepad file which will give you every key in the game, put this in the Elder scrolls V file and go to skyrim and open the console with the \\\"~\\\" key and type \\\"bat key\\\" and you will have every key in the game :). Dawnguard keys are on the notepad file
author: PimpinDaBricks
